Below is a **practical integration roadmap** to add **PageAgent** into your Playwright-based capture system. The goal is **not replacing Playwright**, but **adding an AI layer that helps recover from selector failures**. Treat this as **phases you can implement and validate one by one**.

---

# Target Architecture

```
GitHub PR
   ↓
Step Generator (path-based)
   ↓
Capture Engine (Playwright)
   ↓
Smart Action Layer
   ├─ Try deterministic selector
   ├─ If fail → PageAgent reasoning
   └─ Return corrected selector
   ↓
Playwright executes action
   ↓
Screenshots
   ↓
FFmpeg → Video
   ↓
Upload → R2
   ↓
Comment on PR
```

**Key idea:**
Playwright = execution engine
PageAgent = **UI reasoning assistant**

